                            <comment id="17054927" author="paulk" created="Mon, 9 Mar 2020 12:54:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It appears to break just for property names with exactly 2 uppercase chars but works correctly when &lt;tt&gt;@CompileStatic&lt;/tt&gt; is in play. It&apos;s a bug in BeanUtils.decapitalize for that case.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
